    <item>
      <title>中东停火前景和美国通胀导致油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东停火将缓解紧张局势的前景以及通胀上升的迹象在美联储会议之前打压美国需求前景，油价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 23:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rutter 加入新会员，Pinnacle 增长加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinnacle-hires-royal-london-equities-chief-team-for-new-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinnacle Investment Management Group 将创建一个新的附属机构，该附属机构将容纳皇家伦敦资产管理公司全球股票团队的前成员，其中包括 Peter Rutter，这是该澳大利亚公司下一步国际扩张的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinnacle-hires-royal-london-equities-chief-team-for-new-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 23:37:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着焦点转向美联储会议，亚洲股市下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国利率长期走高的担忧再次引发华尔街抛售，亚洲股市下跌，所有人的目光都集中在周三晚些时候公布的美联储政策决定上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
